{"tid":555421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又到新年 又要比個阿姨煩","createTime":"2018-02-09T11:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T11:58:58.000Z","uid":153684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a54e84d414ec5888be009e636626be6d6ba952b","tid":555421,"uid":153684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"又到新年，我阿姨成40歲人，兩年前終於有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我地一年大概一年見兩三次（年初一，阿婆阿公生日見下面） <br />\n兩年前，佢問我有女朋友未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我：冇啊 呢d野唔急既<br />\n阿姨：快d搵番個喇<br />\n我：哦 我會架喇<br />\n阿姨：搵到個話記得第一時間話我知<br />\n我：好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到上年初一，佢又問我搵到女朋友未<br />\n我：未啊！慢慢黎喇<br />\n阿姨：唔係掛！重未有？<br />\n我：冇所謂喇（心諗：左右姑娘咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n阿姨：唔得咁架喎，再唔搵番個，冇女仔要你<br />\n我：........哦<br />\n心諗 你成40歲人都係上年先有人要 新年流流彩過你話我溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今年又唔知要比佢點樣煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，我老母比佢成5000蚊利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先得個100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}